PM : 300-Unit

Muft Bijli Yojana

"We are launching the PM : Muft Bijli Yojana. Get 300-Unit of Free Bijli every month. This project, with an investment of over Rs. 75,000 crores. Every home of India is eligible to get this 300-Unit scheme.

Shri Narendra Modi
Hon’ble Prime Minister of India
